after learning the 0-1 Knapsack problem one can easily solve the following below problems as they all are based on the same concept:-
1. subset sum problem-----------------------------------done
2. equal sum partition-----------------------------------done
3. count of subset sum with given sum--------------------done
4. minimum subset sum difference-------------------------done
5. target sum--------------------------------------------done
6. number of subsets with the given difference.----------done
7. 0-1 Knapsack------------------------------------------done